    "\\n",
    "## Step 4: Set Up the Project Environment\\n",
    "\\n",
    "Now that the MCP server files are created in `mcp_project/`, you need to set up the environment.\\n",
    "\\n",
    "**Important:** All commands below should be run from the `mcp_project` folder.\\n",
    "\\n",
    "### Using uv (Recommended)\\n",
    "\\n",
    "Open a terminal and run:\\n",
    "\\n",
    "```bash\\n",
